lass="cover" alt="bespoke" src="https://dafen-prod-media.artdafen.com/static/artdafen/bespoke.webp?x-image-process=image/resize,w_1600,limit_0" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="content overflow-hidden" data-v-c2ab6542><div data-v-c2ab6542><h2 class="text-40" data-v-c2ab6542>The Essence of Quality</h2><p class="text-20 mt-20" data-v-c2ab6542> Every painting is meticulously crafted and rigorously inspected before it reaches you </p></div><div class="problem-list row" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="col-6" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="problem-item" data-v-c2ab6542><p class="text-20 font-500" data-v-c2ab6542>Custom Frame Selection</p><p class="text-16 text-gray-600 mt-20" data-v-c2ab6542> Choose from an extensive range of frame styles, finishes, and sizes to complement your décor perfectly. </p></div></div><div class="col-6" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="problem-item" data-v-c2ab6542><p class="text-20 font-500" data-v-c2ab6542>Real-Time Scene Swap</p><p class="text-16 text-gray-600 mt-20" data-v-c2ab6542> Visualize your artwork instantly in living rooms, bedrooms, or gallery settings to find the perfect fit. </p></div></div><div class="col-6" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="problem-item" data-v-c2ab6542><p class="text-20 font-500" data-v-c2ab6542>True-Scale Visualization</p><p class="text-16 text-gray-600 mt-20" data-v-c2ab6542> See your artwork at true scale alongside furniture and décor for precise sizing. </p></div></div><div class="col-6" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="problem-item" data-v-c2ab6542><p class="text-20 font-500" data-v-c2ab6542>Interactive Resize &amp; Crop</p><p class="text-16 text-gray-600 mt-20" data-v-c2ab6542> Easily resize or crop your artwork without losing quality, ensuring it’s just right. </p></div></div><div class="col-6" data-v-c2ab6542><div class="problem-item" data-v-c2ab6542><p class="text-20 font-500" data-v-c2ab6542>Dynamic Style Filters</p><p class="text-16 text-gray-600 mt-20" data-v-c2ab6542> Experiment with matting, wall colors, and lighting presets 