sts)</a></dd><dd data-v-f58e2b09><a href="/contact" class="" data-v-f58e2b09>Contact Us</a></dd><!--]--></dl><dl class="foot-menu" data-v-f58e2b09><dt data-v-f58e2b09>Faqs</dt><!--[--><dd data-v-f58e2b09><a href="/faq/shipping-delivery/how-much-is-shipping-how-long-does-it-take" class="" data-v-f58e2b09>HOW MUCH IS SHIPPING &amp; HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE?</a></dd><dd data-v-f58e2b09><a href="/faq/shipping-delivery/does-free-shipping-include-customs-duties" class="" data-v-f58e2b09>DOES FREE SHIPPING INCLUDE CUSTOMS DUTIES?</a></dd><dd data-v-f58e2b09><a href="/faq/artwork-customization/will-i-see-the-work-before-it-ships" class="" data-v-f58e2b09>WILL I SEE THE WORK BEFORE IT SHIPS?</a></dd><dd data-v-f58e2b09><a href="/faq/returns-refunds/what-is-your-return-policy" class="" data-v-f58e2b09>WHAT IS YOUR RETURN POLICY?</a></dd><!--]--></dl><!--]--></div></div><div class="foot-partner mb-20" data-v-f58e2b09><p class="font-bold text-20 mb-20" data-v-f58e2b09>Cooperative Partner</p><div class="imgs acea-row gap-base" data-v-f58e2b09><a href="https://www.paypal.com" target="_blank" data-v-f58e2b09><img src="/_nuxt/payment-methods.BdBmJY49.png" alt="payment-methods" data-v-f58e2b09></a><a href="https://www.ups.com" target="_blank" data-v-f58e2b09><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="UPS" data-v-f58e2b09></a><a href="https://www.fedex.com" target="_blank" data-v-f58e2b09><img src="/_nuxt/delivery-methods2.BUPgx6Lu.png" alt="FedEx" data-v-f58e2b09></a><a href="https://www.dhl.com" target="_blank" data-v-f58e2b09><img src="/_nuxt/delivery-methods4.0zStmWw6.png" alt="DHL" data-v-f58e2b09></a><a href="https://portraitpainting.com" target="_blank" data-v-f58e2b09><img src="/_nuxt/logo-portrait.CM5ErVM9.png" alt="Portrait" data-v-f58e2b09></a></div><a aria-current="page" href="/" class="router-link-active router-link-exact-active logo-footer" data-v-f58e2b09><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="logo-footer" data-v-f58e2b09></a></div><div class="foot-information" data-v-f58e2b09><div class="text-gray-600 mt-10" data-v-f58e2b09> Our Studio &amp; Fulfillment: A-103-104, Dafen Oil Painting Plaza, Longgang, Shenzhen, Guangdong</div><div class="text-gray-600 mt-10" data-v-f58e2b09> Registered Office: Flat/Rm 502, Arion Commercial Centre, 2-12 Queen&#39;s Road West, Sheung Wan, Hong Kong</div><div class="text-gray-600 mt-10" data-v-f58e2b09> Phone: <a href="tel:+86137 6043 6780" data-v-f58e2b09>+86 137 6043 6780</a></div><div class="text-gray-600 mt-10" data-v-f58e2b09> Email: <a href="mailto:info@artdafen.com" data-v-f58e2b09>info@artdafen.com</a></div></div><div class="copyright mt-10 text-gray-600" style="line-height:1.7;" data-v-f58e2b09> © 2014-2026 ARTDAFEN.COM Museum-caliber oil painting reproductions, exclusively available online. <br data-v-f58e2b09> According to the intellectual property rights, we will only sell artworks in the public domain which means the original artists died no less than 70 years. If you find any paintings listed may have copyright problem, please contact us to remove. </div></footer><footer class="foot-mobile" id="foot-mobile" data-v-e6ac6302 data-v-9da9c936><div class="footer__block-list" data-v-9da9c936><div class="footer__block footer__block--text" data-v-9da9c936><p class="footer__block-title" data-v-9da9c936>ARTDAFEN Vision &amp; Mission</p><div class="prose text-subdued" data-v-9da9c936><p data-v-9da9c936>ARTDAFEN brings exquisite oil paintings into your world, transforming spaces with evocative, gallery-quality art. We offer a curated collection from the heart of the Dafen community, featuring diverse styles and subjects perfect for homes, offices, and beyond. Elevate your everyday and reimagine your world with art that inspires connection and creativity.</p></div></div><!--[--><div class="footer__block--menu footer__block" data-v-9da9c936><p class="footer__block-title" data-v-9da9c936>Agreement</p><ul class="v-stack" role="list" data-v-9da9c936><!--[--><li data-v-9da9c936><a href="/privacy-policy" class=